ovner he is the  recipient of the audubon medal given in recognition of outstanding achievement in the field of conservation and environmental protection see alsoedit list of middlebury college people list of columbia university people litigation involving the wikimedia foundation referencesedit  the worlds billionaires forbes retrieved september     louis bacon forbes retrieved    a b c d e f g h i  louis bacon macro maestrostephen taub july   retrieved july    a b c louis moore bacon forbes  forbes magazine march  retrieved    a b c cynthia pigott married to louis bacon the new york times february   retrieved march     a b dyan machan december   macro moneymaker forbes   louis bacon atradercom june   retrieved march     the worlds billionaires  forbescom forbescom  retrieved november     blevins jason november   billionaire louis bacon battles to protect his ranch from big utilities solarpower plans denver post retrieved december     rohwedder cecilie april   louis bacon tries to turn around taos ski valley wsj retrieved november     meet cash king louis bacon the richest hedge fund manager in london london evening standard april   retrieved november     weddings and celebrations  gabrielle sacconaghi louis bacon new york times february   retrieved november     hooper troy november   conservationist buys states biggest ranch the denver post retrieved march     orton plantation sold to billionaire whqr may   retrieved march     halliday josh may   us billionaire wins high court order over wikipedia defamation london the guardian retrieved may     luisa kroll may   us law protects anonymous speech not billionaires forbes   scannell kara august   louis bacon’s bahamas battle reaches new york court financial times retrieved february     sears neil august   the american hedge fund billionaire who gave £ to the conservatives daily mail london retrieved november     somaiya ravi july   romney holds london fundraiser new york times retrieved november     milliondollar don