set about restoring a natural habitat that had been deteriorating for  years cow neck farm long island new york bacon’s cow neck preserve llc purchased the farm in  and donated a acre conservation easement to the peconic land trust thus preventing development and ensuring the protection of the area’s habitat lyford cay bahamas bacon is involved with the environmental restoration of lyford cay legacy and awardsedit in  he was inducted into institutional investors alphas hedge fund manager hall of fame along with david swensen seth klarman steven cohen kenneth griffin paul tudor jones george soros michael steinhardt jack nash james simmons alfred jones leon levy julian roberston and bruce kovner he is the  recipient of the audubon medal given in recognition of outstanding achievement in the field of conservation and environmental protection see alsoedit list of middlebury college people list of columbia university people litigation involving the wikimedia foundation referencesedit  the worlds billionaires forbes retrieved september     louis bacon forbes retrieved    a b c d e f g h i  louis bacon macro maestrostephen taub july   retrieved july    a b c louis moore bacon forbes  forbes magazine march  retrieved    a b c cynthia pigott married to louis bacon the new york times february   retrieved march     a b dyan machan december   macro moneymaker forbes   louis bacon atradercom june   retrieved march     the worlds billionaires  forbescom forbescom  retrieved november     blevins jason november   billionaire louis bacon battles to protect his ranch from big utilities solarpower plans denver post retrieved december     rohwedder cecilie april   louis bacon tries to turn around taos ski valley wsj retrieved november     meet cash king louis bacon the richest hedge fund manager in london london evening standard april   retrieved november     weddings and celebrations  gabrielle sacconaghi louis bacon new york times february   retrieved november     hooper troy novembe